channel.description:
The remove event handler doesn't check for a full inventory or if you have the item in your inventory and it is stackable, add this in that class

[code=java]
			boolean hasRoomForStackable = inventory.contains(event.getId()) && inventory.get(event.getSlot()).getDefinition().isStackable();
			if (inventory.freeSlots() < 1 && !hasRoomForStackable) {
				inventory.forceCapacityExceeded();
				ctx.breakHandlerChain();
				return;
			}[/code]
